pokedexEntries.gold: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, caring people and shower them with happiness.
pokedexEntries.silver: It grows dispirited if it is not with kind people. It can float in midair without moving its wings.
pokedexEntries.crystal: Although it does not flap its wings very much, it can stay up in the air as it tags along after its trainer.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Togetic is said to be a Pokémon that brings good fortune. When the Pokémon spots someone who is pure of heart, it is said to appear and share its happiness with that person.
